entries.femaleVariant: Oh man, he was shakin' like you were gonna wipe him…
Sorry about that.
Hop in.
Hah! You kiddin'?
I... I wish something bad'd happen to him.
Don't have to pay me, you know.
I know. But dear dad's gonna want those eds.
Don't worry. He'll forget about it.
Keep this up, you'll lose your son for good.
You're pathetic.
You're pathetic, know that?
Steve's my people an' none of your fuckin' business, merc.
Fuckin' same to you. Same to you!
Got nothing to worry about. His brain's scop, won't remember a thing by the time you get back.
Shouldn't talk back like that.
Shouldn't talk back, not yet. Stay chill, lay low. He's all you got for now.
Maybe... Maybe not.
Easy for you to say.
I told 'im he couldn't catch me.
Our place isn't a drunk tank. I actually clean.
Didn't mean how it looks, just who's in it.
Good, good, keep it up. Steve's gonna grow, you know, move out… and you'll be drunk the whole time.
Mhm, go on, make him hate your guts,  you'll never see him again. Guaranteed.
Punk already hates me.
One day you'll wake up wishin' you still had a son. But it'll be too late.
But he will. Always does.
Wait it out. Till you're a bit older.
True. But it's all the advice I got.
Sure he is. But I know how to cobble some together myself.
Ehh, pissant's gotten uppity.
Break your back, spend your lifeblood supporting 'em. He goes off with some vagrant, won't give me the time o' day.
Needs a good talking to. I been nice too long.
Ugh, anything for a drink... Kid'll put me in my grave, I swear.
[Get in]
